race.comment: DASHING SLAY (1) comes here after rocketing around this track over 530m in 30.05, claiming a OPEN by 7 lengths. In winning form and can measure up again. MALLEE BEAUTY (4) boasts a strong record this course with 20 wins and two minors from 25 tries. Scored by 1.75 lengths last time (29.92) in a Special conditions race over 530m at this track. Looks a key chance on best figures. MEPUNGA REWARD (2) is a handy dog who jumped from box 2 last time out and scored by 4.5 lengths at this track (30.03). Ran the fastest time on the program in his latest win. Significant danger. ZELDA COVILHA (3) has strong credentials over this journey.
